{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_15111.jpg","bgm":"bgm23_tokime02","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"(Everyone from the Tokime Clan...?)","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"(Is this...some kind of sightseeing tour...?)"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"...Huh?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":102001,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Tenants, high-end brands, VR...@*Mumble mumble*..."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Shizuka!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102501,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"...Ah, Kagome!"},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"I'm sorry we had to meet up with you like this..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"No! If anything, it made you stand out@so you were easy to find..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"...So, what exactly is this?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Well...to put it simply..."},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"\"Learning about the world.\""},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Learning about...the world, is it?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"You want to interview me and the rest@of the Tokime Clan, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"So, I thought it would be best@to have you come here."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"I see...so, for what purpose, exactly...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"From my experiences in Kamihama so far,@I have learned..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"First of all, simply put, \"the world is vast.\""},{"chara":[{"id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Those raised deep in the mountains, like@myself and some of the branch family Diviners,"},{"chara":[{"id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"didn't understand that."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"...No, rather, we understood it in words,@but didn't truly grasp it."},{"chara":[{"id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"You know our clan's mission, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Um... \"To protect the Land of the Rising Sun\"?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Yes...and, to \"protect the wishes we made.\""},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"To fulfill that mission, we must look to the future."},{"chara":[{"id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"To do that, we must understand the Land of the@Rising Sun as it is today."},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Understanding the present leads to understanding@the future."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"I see...so that's why you're studying society."},{"chara":[{"id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"The situation surrounding Magical Girls is still calm@for now."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"And here, in Sakae Ward, is the perfect place@to catch a glimpse of the modern world! "},{"chara":[{"id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"...Right?"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Well, yes, I guess so..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"By knowing the present like this, we can foresee@hints to grasp the future!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_060.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"I can't take this anymore—!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"W-whats wrong?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"These questions are too advanced, I'm lost...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"Maybe this was too over-stimulating..."},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"Everyone, you all have an incredible thirst for@knowledge."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Th-this is hardly a good thing!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"...Then, how about you answer instead, Shizuka?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"...Me?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":770200,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Ah, there you are!@I have something I want to ask you about!"},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Wait, what?!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
